data.title: Eurovision Song Contest 1964 Results
data.text:
Eurovision Song Contest 1964 Results Page

For all those people who are interested in the Eurovision Song Contest, here are the results for 1964.

Links to other Pages. More Links at bottom of page.

The 1964 Eurovision Song Contest was held at the Tivoli Concert Hall in Copenhagen, Denmark on Saturday 21 March 1964. Presented by Lotte Waever.

This table is interactive! To sort a column, just click on any of the column heading. Click again for reverse sort.

The winner was Italy.
